bug_data.description:
The python-defaults package has been updated in Debian, and those changes
        need to be merged into Ubuntu.  An automatic merge was
        attempted, but was not able to process all of the changes.

        The output from the automatic attempt can be found here:

        http://people.ubuntu.com/~scott/merge/review/python-defaults

        Some documentation about the output can be found here:

        http://people.ubuntu.com/~scott/merge/README
bug_data.title: Unmerged changes from Debian
